                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The hag gazes upon a creature, afflicting it with a gnawing sense of impending doom, with a result depending on its @Check[will|dc:20|options:inflicts:frightened,inflicts:slowed] save. The target doesn't need to be able to see the sea hag.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is frightened 1 and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slowed 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> As failure, but the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2} and slowed 1 for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
