            "publicNotes": "<p>Hags are malevolent predators who use magic and manipulation to lure children and young adults into their clutches. They seek out targets who are unhappy, innocent, or otherwise vulnerable, preying on their weaknesses before snatching them up. A sea hag has the upper half of a humanoid and the lower half of an octopus, with translucent skin and glowing lights visible beneath their flesh.</p>",
